comments: VanVleet (TOR) briefly places his arm on Maxey's (PHI) front at the start of his drive, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) is set in Maxey's (PHI) path and marginal contact occurs during the screen attempt.
Harden (PHI) and Achiuwa (TOR) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) is moving alongside Harden's (PHI) path to the basket and marginal contact occurs when Harden collapses his left arm against his side and comes together with Trent Jr.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending violation by Anunoby (TOR) is confirmed.
Siakam (TOR) firms up and makes marginal contact with Maxey (PHI) during the screen attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) makes contact to Harden's (PHI) right arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
After the screen attempt, Harris (PHI) moves along with Siakam (TOR) on his path to the basket.
Trent Jr. (TOR) and Maxey (PHI) mutually engage and disengage.
Replay review of the foul called on Harden (PHI) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Harden makes contact to Achiuwa's (TOR) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Anunoby (TOR) makes incidental contact with Harris (PHI) as both players go for the loose ball.
VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental arm contact with Harris (PHI) as he attempts to dislodge the ball from Harris.
Trent Jr. (TOR) and Harris (PHI) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Green (PHI) briefly places his arm on Siakam's (TOR) front at the start of his drive toward the rim.
Harris (PHI) and VanVleet (TOR) mutually engage and disengage after the screen attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Achiuwa (TOR) loses control of the ball and is the last to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Anunoby (TOR) briefly holds Embiid (PHI) as he is rolling towards the rim.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact with Maxey (PHI) during the screen attempt.
Embiid (PHI) makes contact to Anunoby's (TOR) head that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact with Achiuwa (TOR) during the screen attempt.
Green (PHI) and Anunoby (TOR) make marginal contact as both players go for the loose ball.
